title: Ep. 471 - Diwali At Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sodhi and others are successful in handing over Peter to the police. Its Diwali time and Tapu Sena takes blessings from everybody.

title: Ep. 472 - A Morning Walk? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya is worried for her brother when he doesn't answer her call. Jetha is scolded by Chachaji for waking up really late. He is asked to go to the park for a jog where he dozes off.

title: Ep. 473 - Sundar's Plot Scheme - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sundar comes home to meet his sister Daya. Daya arranges a feast of food for her brother. Later, Sundar, in a conversation with Jetha is trying to lure him into greediness.

title: Ep. 474 - An Understanding Jetha  - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya is shocked when Jetha is ready to buy a flat. He explains that he didn't accept any deal from Sundar to avoid any sort of problems. He cares for their relationship and doesn't want to spoil it.

title: Ep. 475 - Sodhi Gives The Token Amount - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide and Sodhi go for a ride when Bhide tells him about the flat. Sodhi is ready to buy the flat and gives the token amount. Sundar curses Jetha for not buying the plot from him and the trouble has just begun.

title: Ep. 476 - New Gifts For Bhide - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide is in trouble as both Sodhi and Jethalal have given him their tokens. Bhide realizes that he has done a huge mistake. He goes to Jethalal to convince him but doesn't succeed. Madhavi takes the step to convince Sodhi. Will they succeed?

title: Ep. 477 - Who Will Get The Flat ? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Chanda Ramani's flat is on sale and Roshan Singh, as well as Jethalal, wants to buy it. They both have paid token money to Bhide and Madhvi. Now the problem is none of them is trying to back off and let go off the flat.

title: Ep. 478 - Jethalal And Soni's Irrationality - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide is sandwiched between Jethalal and Sodi's demands and ways of convincing him. Their irrational behavior has led to big trouble for Bhide. Whereas the children and women of Gokuldham seem to be more sensible than the two fighting for the flat.

title: Ep. 479 - Bhide Is No Longer The Middleman - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Finally, Chanda Ramani calls back Bhide for updates on his apartment. Bhide explains him everything and after listening, he decides to hold an auction, whoever bids the highest gets the apartment. Bhide coveys this news to both of them.

title: Ep. 480 - Auction Day At Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Chanda Ramami finally arrives at Gokuldham for the auction and meets everyone after a long time. In due course, the auction begins with Jethalal bidding first. It carries on for a while. The person who bids the highest astonishes everyone.

title: Ep. 486 - Krishnaben Khakhrawala In Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The famous Krishnaben arrives in Gokuldham with her khakhra's. Daya seeing her gets excited and praises her. Even Taarak tastes and loves it. Later, Taarak and Anjali have a little fight over a petty issue.

title: Ep. 487 - A Bad Day For All - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethlal's suit does not fit him but it's not the same with Daya. Champaklal hurt his feet while climbing the stairs and screams, listening to which everybody comes to rescue. In seeing them in that attire all are stunned.

title: Ep. 488 - Jethalal's Anger and Realization - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The expensive cheque is spoilt by Daya but unintentionally. Jethalal out of anger comments harsh and mean things to her. Daya gets upset but later takes a stand to be not looked down upon. Jethalal realizes his wrong behavior.

title: Ep. 489 - It's Not That Easy - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal called Daya several times but she did not receive the call. He rushes home to ask for forgiveness and to say sorry. He reaches home, but she does not open the door. He opts for stupid ways to get her to open the door.

title: Ep. 490 - Gokuldham Struggles With Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: In due course of time, all of Gokuldham suspects the weird behavior of Jethalal and finally gets to know about the whole situation. Everybody decides to help him out and get Daya to talk to him and asks Sodi to get inside the house somehow.
